false,"explanation":"[Narrative Speculation] Imports unsupported assumptions about author motivation or future plans."},{"id":"D","text":"It treats the passage as a chronological biography, ignoring the pivot from consensus to challenge that organizes the discussion across the full paragraph in context as written.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Structural Inversion] Reverses the actual sequence of ideas the passage develops."}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'Step 1 — Identify the passage organization
