ice matches the passage''s rhetorical architecture from framework through evidence to qualified implications."},{"id":"D","text":"It accurately describes the concession in sentence two but ignores how the passage integrates that concession into a broader qualified defense in the closing sentences in context.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Structural Inversion] [Partial Scope] Describes only part of the passage, ignoring its overall trajectory."}]'::jsonb, 'C', 'Step 1 — Identify the passage organization
